name: Alex the Abominable
description:
Alex the Abominable is a full colour, paperback comic book with = action, adventure, mayhem, monsters all set around...a family road trip with snowman, monsters, Aliens and Robots.

Starring the smartest kid in the Universe called Alex.

Also two smaller adventures include 'Alex On Patrol' - Alex battles with a crazed robot and paperwork hungry Aliens!

And

'Alex Escapes' - Our young heroine is stranded upon an Aztec like planet surrounded by creatures that want to gobble her up!
